# Normalize line endings for all text files to LF so Prettier, ESLint,
# and CI (which runs on Linux) all agree. Windows developers can keep
# CRLF in their working tree (Git handles the translation on checkout
# via core.autocrlf), but what goes *into* the repo is always LF.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Keep binary assets byte-for-byte.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
